#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Syncing…"
msgstr "Synchronisation en cours…"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Sync completed successfully!"
msgstr "Synchronisation terminée avec succès !"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "An error occurred during sync."
msgstr "Erreur lors de la synchronisation."

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Start sync now? This may take several minutes."
msgstr ""
"Lancer la synchronisation maintenant ? Cela peut prendre plusieurs minutes."

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Settings saved."
msgstr "Paramètres enregistrés."

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Interactive map of French schools."
msgstr "Carte interactive des établissements scolaires français."

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Utilisation"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Add the map to a page or post with the shortcode:"
msgstr "Ajoutez la carte dans une page ou un article avec le shortcode :"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Or use the \"French Schools Map\" block in the Gutenberg editor."
msgstr "Ou utilisez le bloc « French Schools Map » dans l'éditeur Gutenberg."

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Available attributes"
msgstr "Attributs disponibles"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Attribute"
msgstr "Attribut"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Default"
msgstr "Défaut"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Description"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Map height"
msgstr "Hauteur de la carte"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Initial zoom level"
msgstr "Niveau de zoom initial"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Types: Ecole, Collège, Lycée (comma-separated)"
msgstr "Types : Ecole, Collège, Lycée (séparés par des virgules)"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Department name to filter"
msgstr "Nom du département à filtrer"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Academy name to filter"
msgstr "Nom de l'académie à filtrer"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Public or Privé"
msgstr "Public ou Privé"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Show filter panel"
msgstr "Afficher le panneau de filtres"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Show search bar"
msgstr "Afficher la barre de recherche"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Enable marker clustering"
msgstr "Activer le clustering de marqueurs"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Default settings"
msgstr "Paramètres par défaut"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid ""
"Set the default geographic filter. Choose either an academy or a department "
"(mutually exclusive). This setting applies when the shortcode has no "
"departement/academie attribute."
msgstr ""
"Définissez le filtre géographique par défaut. Choisissez soit une académie, "
"soit un département (mutuellement exclusifs). Ce réglage s'applique quand le "
"shortcode n'a pas d'attribut departement/academie."

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Default academy"
msgstr "Académie par défaut"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "All (no filter)"
msgstr "Toutes (pas de filtre)"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid ""
"If an academy is selected, it automatically groups the corresponding "
"departments."
msgstr ""
"Si une académie est sélectionnée, elle regroupe automatiquement les "
"départements correspondants."

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Default department"
msgstr "Département par défaut"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid ""
"The department takes priority over the academy. If a department is chosen, "
"the academy is ignored."
msgstr ""
"Le département a priorité sur l'académie. Si un département est choisi, "
"l'académie est ignorée."

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Save settings"
msgstr "Enregistrer les paramètres"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Data synchronisation"
msgstr "Synchronisation des données"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php french-schools-map.php (shortcode HTML)
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Statut"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Last sync"
msgstr "Dernière synchronisation"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Never"
msgstr "Jamais"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Records"
msgstr "Enregistrements"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Next sync"
msgstr "Prochaine synchronisation"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Not scheduled"
msgstr "Non planifiée"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Sync now"
msgstr "Synchroniser maintenant"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid ""
"The sync downloads the full school directory (~69,000 establishments) from "
"the Open Data portal of the Ministry of National Education. This operation "
"may take several minutes."
msgstr ""
"La synchronisation télécharge l'intégralité de l'annuaire (~69 000 "
"établissements) depuis le portail Open Data du Ministère de l'Éducation "
"Nationale. Cette opération peut prendre plusieurs minutes."

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Idle"
msgstr "En attente"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Running…"
msgstr "En cours…"

#: includes/class-fsm-admin.php
msgid "Success"
msgstr "Succès"

#: includes/class-fsm-local-db.php
msgid "A sync is already in progress."
msgstr "Une synchronisation est déjà en cours."

#: includes/class-fsm-local-db.php
msgid "Cannot open CSV file."
msgstr "Impossible d'ouvrir le fichier CSV."

#: includes/class-fsm-local-db.php
msgid "CSV has no header row."
msgstr "Le fichier CSV n'a pas de ligne d'en-tête."

#: includes/class-fsm-local-db.php
msgid "Only %1$d records (minimum %2$d). Aborting."
msgstr "Seulement %1$d enregistrements (minimum %2$d). Abandon."

#: includes/class-fsm-local-db.php
msgid "CSV missing required columns: %s"
msgstr "Colonnes obligatoires manquantes dans le CSV : %s"

#: includes/class-github-updater.php
msgid "Unable to rename the update folder. Please retry or update manually."
msgstr ""
"Impossible de renommer le dossier de mise à jour. Veuillez réessayer ou "
"mettre à jour manuellement."

